(1) Hun-pan e5 phiau-chun2
Beh hun-pan u7 2 e5 phiau-hun2, chit8 e5 si7 eng7 ni5-hoe3 lai5 pun, koh chit8 e5 si7 eng7 hak8-lek8 lai5 pun, beh hun-pan tek-khak tioh8 chiau3 chit 2 e5 phiau-chun2. Ti7 Bi2-kok u7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 keng-koe3 chhi3-giam7 chiah hou7 hak8-seng jip8 pan, chit khoan2 ti7 Jit8-pun2 e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 si7 bo5 hoat-tou7 thang si-heng5.
(2) Hun-pan e5 hoat-tou7
Chu2-jit8-oh8 chi3-chio2 tioh8 seng pun cho3 4 pan, chit 4 pan chiah koh hun khah se3-pan. (1) Iu3-lian5 pan, siu-iong5 3 hoe3 khi2 kau3 7-8 hoe3 e5 hak8-seng, chit e5 iu3-lian5-pan, na7 e7-tang3, koh pun cho3 2 pan, chit8-pan si7 4-5 hoe3 i2-ha7 e5 gin2-na2 long2 be7 hiau2 thak8 e5, koh chit8-pan si7 sio2-khoa2 e7 hiau2 thak8 e5 6-7 hoe3 e5 gin2-na2, chit 2 pan cho3 chit8 hoe2 ka3 ia7 ho2, chong2-si7 chin7-liong7 pun cho3 2 pan ka3 khah ho2. Ti7 Bi2-kok, chit8 e5 iu3-lian5-pan e5 lai7-bin7 u7 koh chit8-pan io5-na5 pan, teh siu-iong5 sin3-tou5 e5 ang5-enn-a2. <BR> (2) Siau3-lian5 pan: siu-iong5 9-12 hoe3 e5 hak8-seng.<BR> (3) Chheng-lian5 pan: che tioh8 koh hun 2 pan; chit8 pan si7 13-15 hoe3, koh chit8-pan si7 16-18 hoe3. <BR>(4) Seng5-lian5 pan: siu-iong5 18 hoe3 i2-siong7 e5 lam5-lu2, chit 4 toa7 pan tek-khak tioh8 pun, na7 bo5 teh ka3 e5 si5 e7 kam2-kak put-chi2 bo5 li7-pian7, chiau3 an2-ni lai5 pun e5 lang5-sou3 m7-thang chhiau-koe3 15 mia5, choe3 li2-siong2 si7 8 e5 chi2 10 e5 e5 tiong-kan.
