(4) Seng-kip
U7 oan5-choan5 hun-pan e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 keng-koe3 1-2 ni5 au7 tek-khak tioh8 hou7 hak8-seng seng-koe3 khah koan5 e5 pan, 3-4 ni5 ku2 tng5-tng5 ke3-siok8 toa3 ti7 kang7 pan si7 m7 ho2, chin7-liong7 m7 thang hou7 hak8-seng sit-bang7, tioh8 chiam7-chiam7 ka7 seng koe3 khah koan5 e5 pan. Long2-chong2 e5 kho3-theng5 na7 long2 oe7-hiau2 thak8 e5 lang5, ia7 tioh8 chhin-chhiunn7 phou2-thong e5 hak8-hau7, eng7 pit-giap8 cheng3-su hou7 in si7 khah ho2.
(5) Hou7 hak8-seng jip8 pan e5 kang
Sin hak8-seng lai5 e5 si5, hau7-tiunn2 tioh8 liam5-pinn hou7 i jip8 ti7 tu2-ho2 e5 pan, m7-thang hou7 gin2-na2 ka-ki7 loan7-lai5. U7 si5 hau7-tiunn2 kap tai7-ke chham-siong5 liau2, tiann7 tioh8 pun-pan e5 hoat-tou7, a2-si7 hak8-seng beh pun jip8 pan e5 su7, koh mui2 2 kou2 geh8, hau7-tiunn2 tek-khak tioh8 siau7-kai3 sin-jip8 seng e5 mia5, kap in e5 pan-mia5 hou7 long2-chong2 e5 hak8-seng chai.
(6) Hun pan e5 mia5
Kok pan e5 beng5-chheng m7-thang eng7 kau3-oan5 e5 mia5 lai5 ho7. Jit8-pun2 e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 kau3-oan5 chin gau5 oann7 lang5, na7 an2-ni kinn3-na7 oann7 kau3-oan5 e5 si5, tioh8 oann7 in e5 pan-mia5. Sou2-i2 pan-mia5 tioh8 eng7 pat8-mih8 lai5 ho7, phi3-ju7 na7 eng7 hoe e5 mia5, thang hou7 mui5-pan, a2-si7 lan5 pan, na7 eng7 tek-heng7 ho7 mia5 thang ho7 sin3 pan, a2-si7 jim2 pan, a2-si7 bo5 ho7 mia5 chi2 u7 cho3 te7 1 pan, te7 2 pan ia7-si7 ho2, put-ko3 na7 u7 an2-ni ho7 mia5, hak8-seng toa3 2 ni5-au7 na7 cho3 bo5 koh lai5, i ka-ki7 ia7 eng2-oan2 e7-ki3-tit i si7 bat ti7 sin3-pan a2-si7 lan5-pan, si7 chin ho2 e5 su7.
